dark-aeth.description:
ZALERIA.

dark-aeth.title: Cosmic Katy Suspender Dress
dark-aeth.description:
COSMIC KATY. 
It’s not you, it’s your star sign.  
- Soft stretch fabric. 
- High neck. 
- Large vegan leather collar. 
- Adjustable vegan leather straps. 
 - Mesh underlay. 
 - Sleeve details. 
 - Skater skirt. 
- Fitted. 
 Be a celestial beauty in our ‘Cosmic Katy’ Suspender dress. Conjured in soft, stretch fabric with stretch mesh underlay to create the perfect fit. Complete with a skater skirt bottom, adjustable faux leather straps and faux leather collar you’ll feel outta this world. A staple piece for any star gazer.  
 Match with a witch brim and some killer boots to complete the look!

dark-aeth.title: Grave Rebellion Dress [B]
dark-aeth.description: Cause a storm in our 'Grave Rebellion' dress. Conjured from super soft and stretchy material to ensure it hugs you in all the right places! Features a pentagram pull, statement zip down the front, cap sleeves and detachable straps. This angsty statement piece is a must-have in any gothic wardrobe!

dark-aeth.title: 4th Dimension Dress
dark-aeth.description: Be closer to the moon any hour of the day/night with the '4th Dimension' dress. Super soft fabric with just the right amount of stretch - for a flattering and comfortable fit. With a low neckline to expose just the right amount of skin, thin straps with lace-up detail to chest and statement long sleeves. An essential piece - easy to wear and goes with anything!

dark-aeth.title: Anti Everything Zip Dress
dark-aeth.description: Awaken your inner anarchist in our ‘Anti everything’ zip dress. Conjured in super stretch woven fabric for the perfect fit. Featuring a statement O-ring full length zip closure, statement straps and detachable, fishnet sleeves with metal hard wear this dress is bold.Looks deadly with your fav chunky boots and choker!

dark-aeth.title: To Dust Kimono-Sleeve Dress [B]
dark-aeth.description: It's always the witching hour somewhere; the enchanted 'To Dust' kimono-sleeve dress brings you an elegant look mixed with haunted house vibes. Summoned by soft-stretch lace fabric that follows your silhouette - for a flattering fit and perfect comfort. With long flared sleeves. Complete with a high neck, cold shoulders and delicate trims. Versatile and easy to style; perfect for dinner dates, adventures out the crypt or hitting the nightlife - any day of the week!

dark-aeth.title: Phenomena Lace Maxi Dress [B]
dark-aeth.description: Too much of a good thing can be fun! Channeling a seductive vibe with its figure-hugging fit, the 'Phenomena' lace maxi dress has been constructed using the most decadent lace for ultimate feel + comfort. With a high collar, keyhole detail on the chest and statement sleeves. Fits like a glove - purrfect for date night, parties or just yer daily/nightly adventures.

dark-aeth.title: Jovana Collar & Ring Dress
dark-aeth.description: Which sin did you commit today? Make everyone else envious in our 'Jovana' collar and ring dress; conjured using a soft fabric which stretches to perfection for a comfortable yet flattering fit. No detail has been spared - features an exaggerated collar, short sleeves, cut-out and ring details and skater skirt. A sinful statement piece to transcend yer look - bound to make even the dark lord take notice.

dark-aeth.title: Scarlet Kisses Dress
dark-aeth.description: Are you a daydreamer or a night thinker? Get enchanted by the 'Scarlet Kisses' dress; in a lusciously soft fabric for perfect comfort and fit. Featuring a bardot neck with long sleeves and extra flared cuffs. Perfect for dinner dates, gigs, late-night promenades or simply a day out of the crypt!

dark-aeth.title: Siouxsie Dress
dark-aeth.description: Channel your inner badass with the 'Siouxsie' dress; composed of a soft stretch material for a flattering + comfortable fit, guaranteed to turn heads when yer out! With statement front straps connecting to a choker and low back to show off some skin. Very versatile and perfect from dusk to dawn!

dark-aeth.title: She's Laced Lace Dress
dark-aeth.description: Bringing you a perfect balance of sweetness to the dark abyss the 'She's Laced' lace dress; conjured using an ultra-soft stretch lace dress for a dreamy fit. Complete with a cute cap sleeve, ruffle accents, high neckline with collar and button up front. Purrfect for play-dates, picnics under the moon and dinner dates alike!

dark-aeth.title: Violet Lace Dress
dark-aeth.description: The night is young and full of mystery. Fall in lust with our 'Violet' lace dress; conjured using a decadent lace and woven material with some extra stretch, to fit ya like a glove. No detail has been spared - featuring a low neckline, 3/4 length sleeves and delicate lace trims. This lil statement piece is truly gothic perfection - designed to help you hex all day then slay the night away.

dark-aeth.title: Temperance Lace Babydoll
dark-aeth.description: In dreams we enter a world that is entirely our own. The 'Temperance' lace dress is a delicate and seductive statement piece perfect for a romantic day look. This dreamy dress is conjured using custom made nylon-base lace which stretches around the body for a comfortable and flattering fit. Fall in love with yourself in this lil' gothic must-have complete with high neckline, lace trim detail, capped sleeves and floaty babydoll skirt.

dark-aeth.title: Hecate Lace Maxi Dress
dark-aeth.description: In dreams, we enter a world that is entirely our own. The 'Hecate' lace maxi dress is a delicate and seductive statement piece perfect for a romantic day look. This dreamy dress is conjured using custom-made soft-touch lace which stretches around the body for a comfortable and flattering fit. Fall in love with yourself in this lil' gothic must-have complete with a high neckline and statement waterfall sleeves. Looks great dressed up or down - whatever your mood/moon wants!

dark-aeth.title: Eve Hallows Mesh Dress
dark-aeth.description: If you got it, haunt it. Feel every part divine in the 'Eve Hallows' mesh dress - a dark and decadent combination of sheer mesh with a modesty slip, the perfect dress for any dark vamp! Complete with deadly details - exaggerated collar, delicate trims, button plaquet and capped sleeves. You'll be ready to slay in this statement piece - perfect from Dusk to Dawn!

dark-aeth.title: Arch Angelz Masked Top
dark-aeth.description: Be ready to take on the elements in our 'Arch Angelz' masked top. Conjured from a soft material for a comfortable but flattering bit. Featuring long sleeves with cut-out accents, metal buckles and mask detail. This must-have top is a dream to style and will have you feeling like a badass babe all day!

dark-aeth.title: Meridian Long Sleeve Top
dark-aeth.description: Make the stars align with our ‘Meridian’ long sleeve top. Crafted in super soft, stretch cotton it’s basic but never boring. With a large zip detail, high neck and vegan leather straps it’s the perfect staple for any star gazers wardrobe.

dark-aeth.title: Orb Crop Top
dark-aeth.description: Drape your celestial self in our ‘Orb’ Crop top. Crafted in super soft, stretch fabric with mesh inserts and cold shoulder details. Finished with an XL mercury glyph pendant zipper it’s basic but never boring. The perfect piece to style into any stargazers wardrobe.

dark-aeth.title: Jovie Top
dark-aeth.description: Stand out in our ‘Jovie’ top; Crafted with soft super stretch fabric to create the perfect figure hugging fit, with a keyhole detail, cut out fishnet sleeves detailed with straps this piece is a staple and a statement. Goes well with almost anything - a perfect wardrobe staple and must-have!

dark-aeth.title: Manticore Long Sleeve Top
dark-aeth.description: Look devilishly good in the 'Manticore' long sleeve top; conjured using a super-soft jersey fabric which stretches to perfection for a flattering body huggin' fit. Features a round neck, long sleeves, mesh panel and asymmetrical body. A classic staple piece that looks great with all your fav dark looks. The purrrfect addition to any dark souls collection - looks great dressed up or down depending on your mood/moon!

dark-aeth.title: Orbit Hockey Top
dark-aeth.description: Run circles around mainstream looks with our ‘Orbit’ Hockey top. Crafted in soft cotton jersey with a large, statement mesh Mercury glyph and additional mesh bands around the bottom and sleeves. A perfect piece to layer with and a staple in any stargazers wardrobe.

dark-aeth.title: Double Crossed Long Sleeve Top
dark-aeth.description: Ready to chill/thrill/kill any hour of the day with our 'Double Crossed' top. Super-soft fabric with just the right amount of stretch, a high neckline, fitted body with cold-shoulders and cut-out detail on the chest to expose the right amount of skin and silver cross hardware. An essential piece - easy to wear and goes with anything

dark-aeth.title: Lost In Sin Zip Top
dark-aeth.description: Ready to ghoul'n'roll with the 'Lost In Sin' statement top - featuring a lush crushed-velvet body with a large pentagram to the chest, full zip-front, slightly cropped and adjustable shoulder straps. A perfect easy go-to-piece for any day or night!

dark-aeth.title: Dungeoness Hoodie
dark-aeth.description: Are you all about sweater-weather life? Get extra cozy with the 'Dungeoness' super-soft jersey hood-dress! Complete with a fitted longline body, oversized hood with drawstrings, extra-long sleeves, front pockets and hanky hem statement for some extra drama. A best-of-both-worlds basic; equally perfect for lounging as it is for a night out! Wear on its own or layer as your mood/moon desires!

dark-aeth.title: In The Shadows Cloak
dark-aeth.description: Life is one big ritual; the spellbinding 'In The Shadows' statement cloak is conjured of the softest stretch-fabric; for superior comfort and fit. Featuring a draping body, oversized hood, and open front. Ideal for layering - transforms your daily routine to a magical expression - perfect for festivals, midnight ceremonies, and hot dates.

dark-aeth.title: Draco Cowl Hoodie
dark-aeth.description: An easy to style staple-piece; 'Draco' is a pull-over hoodie with an extra large hood with cowl neck, long sleeves, and hanky hem statement. Smooth cotton-jersey so its perfect for day-to-day wear - or anytime u leave the crypt!

dark-aeth.title: Bite Me Fishnet Bolero
dark-aeth.description: Don't fear to fall - just get back up or you risk not getting anywhere at all. Hot AF fishnet 'Bite Me' bolero in a soft nylon mix with super stretch; wide neckline with long sleeves. Purrfect for your black on black wardrobe.

dark-aeth.title: You Are Warped Sweater
dark-aeth.description: Gettin' real cozy - the 'You Are Warped' sweater in a soft-touch knit; with a hood with pull strings, an asymmetric hem and long sleeves. The long length makes it versatile AF; wear over leggings/denim or on its own as a dress!

dark-aeth.title: Yasumi Mesh Skirt
dark-aeth.description:
- Soft, stretch fabric. 
 - 4 adjustable, removable suspender straps. 
- Built in shorts. 
- Wide waistband. 
 - Fitted.

dark-aeth.title: Death Star Maxi Skirt
dark-aeth.description: Embrace your dark side with our ‘Death Star’ Maxi skirt. Crafted in soft, stretch material with a mini underskirt and long mesh overskirt featuring a hanky hem. Simple, but never basic - a perfect staple for any dark wardrobe!

dark-aeth.title: No Feelings Jeans
dark-aeth.description: Live your best cold hearted life in our ‘No Feelings’ jeans. Conjured from soft stretch material for that killer figure hugging fit, detailed with studs, cut out mesh inserts and a zip these are the perfect staple piece for any dark wardrobe.

dark-aeth.title: Azazel Washed Jeans
dark-aeth.description: As black as your soul, the 'Azazel' washed jeans feature a soft-touch cotton-mix denim for a perfect fit and comfortable wear. Complete with lace-up detail, mesh panels with straps, zip accents and belt loops. Hell yeah!

dark-aeth.title: State Of Calamity Skirt
dark-aeth.description: Always in control with the 'State of Calamity' skirt with just the right balance of detail. Featuring a soft stretch fabric for a flattering + comfortable fit; with an asymmetric hem and statement straps with pentagram hardware. Adorned with D-rings and zipped side for easy on/off. Easy to dress up or down, depending on your mood [or moon]
